casebody.data:
Glock, Appellant, v. Hammond, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. December 23, 1891.) Appeal from third district court. . Action by Edward Glock against John Hammond.

Argued before Bookstaver and Bisohoff, JJ.

M. Van Hovenburgh, for appellant. F. If. Smith, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
